# Tailoring & Fashion Design App – Project Prompt

## Project Goal 

To build a mobile-friendly tailoring and fashion design app that allows users to create, customize, and manage clothing designs while connecting with professional tailors.

## Target Users

* Fashion design students
* Professional tailors
* Boutique owners
* Individuals who want custom-made clothes
* Customers who need measurements stored digitally

## Main Features

* User registration and login
* Profile creation (customer or tailor)
* Digital body measurement storage
* Design gallery (browse clothing styles)
* Custom outfit designer (choose fabric, color, style)
* Order placement system
* Order tracking (Pending, In Progress, Completed)
* Appointment booking with tailor
* Image upload for design inspiration
* Notifications for order updates

## Pages / Layout

* Home Page (Introduction and featured designs)
* Sign Up / Login Page
* User Dashboard
* Tailor Dashboard
* Design Gallery Page
* Custom Design Page
* Measurement Page
* Orders Page
* Booking / Appointment Page
* Profile Settings Page

## UI Style Requirements

* Clean and modern fashion-inspired design
* Soft neutral colors (beige, white, brown, black)
* Elegant fonts (stylish but readable)
* High-quality clothing images
* Card-based layout for designs
* Responsive design (mobile-first approach)
* Simple navigation bar at top or bottom

## State Management Needs

* Store logged-in user session
* Save user measurements
* Manage order status updates
* Store selected designs temporarily before checkout
* Real-time updates for order progress

## Authentication Needs

* Users must sign up and log in
* Email and password authentication
* Role-based access (Customer or Tailor)
* Password reset option
* Secure data storage

## Design Constraints

* Must be mobile-friendly
* Must load quickly
* Simple and easy-to-use interface
* Secure user data protection
* Follow modern UI/UX best practices
* Must work properly on both Android and iPhone browse
